    <h4>Joel Patterson</h4>
    <h5>Executive Producer</h5>
    <p>As the former Executive Producer/Showrunner of History's Pawn Stars, Patterson is a passionate storyteller inspired and driven by dynamic formats. Patterson is also the creator and Co-Executive Producer of History’s Counting Cars - which remains the network's highest rated unscripted series premiere. He began his career in broadcast journalism honing his craft at 60 Minutes, 48 Hours, and MSNBC Documentaries.  He has also produced series for WE tv, IFC, Discovery, A&E and Science.</p>
